{"tid":2080024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籲罷習惹禍 前政協發斷六親聲明","createTime":"2020-06-26T07:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T07:14:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3bd96fcc7f454558b205d33ee80f99e3a878e1","tid":2080024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200626/D3YIA5TAOOFSR4LKZSXJ4NGV5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200626%2FD3YIA5TAOOFSR4LKZSXJ4NGV5Q%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=40ff0ec9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200626%2FD3YIA5TAOOFSR4LKZSXJ4NGV5Q%2F&h=ab546ddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200626/D3YIA5TAOOFSR4LKZSXJ4NGV5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n籲罷習惹禍 前政協發斷六親聲明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ogF85co8v62eg4ipb_m1-HCrACU=/190x128/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NORQZYEF7NFX7T4MT35BTMT56A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FogF85co8v62eg4ipb_m1-HCrACU%3D%2F190x128%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNORQZYEF7NFX7T4MT35BTMT56A.gif&h=2edf130d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王瑞琴不滿中共株連無辜。<br />\n<br />\n前青海省政協委員王瑞琴早前因公開呼籲罷免國家主席習近平，其家人遭中共當局威脅，公司資產也被凍結。為保護家人，她日前發表聲明與家人斷絕關係，並指當局「株連無辜，人所不齒」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥「株連無辜 人所不齒」<br />\n<br />\n據自由亞洲電台報道<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n她的公司資產被凍結。<br />\n<br />\n王瑞琴說，有鑑於此，她聲明與所有親屬斷絕關係，不再與包括孩子、家人、同胞兄弟姐妹及其家人、所有具有血緣關係的族親及其家人往來。她在聲明中強調，自己追求民主、反對暴政，所涉言行舉止皆屬個人行為，與他人無關，並願意承擔全部責任。雖然中國當局「株連無辜，人所不齒」，但不會奏效。王瑞琴指出，從家人被騷擾及公司資產被凍結來看，她懷疑中國當局正對她羅織罪名。稍後，她將選擇合適時機公開詳情。<br />\n<br />\n現年56歲的王瑞琴，曾<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n，並呼籲兩會代表、委員罷免習近平。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"bfaacc39541c29971ada833d58ea5bb128b1f223","tid":2080024,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2020-05/image-1590193738279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2020-05%2Fimage-1590193738279.jpg&h=bf3b5867&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8032978b589410e4fbff6fffc81dc5e5c5df96f1","tid":2080024,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jjaqquLwkaXee0PP38zMoQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/10dfb3cea209ca4d008da8d30e7be2a8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjjaqquLwkaXee0PP38zMoQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F10dfb3cea209ca4d008da8d30e7be2a8&h=01761f57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdfd6f6224ac2bfdac198ffb348d2743b2d71e83","tid":2080024,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G08DYrW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG08DYrW.jpg&h=c6b0925f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d61a511ddeded06471b41b7b228743a94b0e8","tid":2080024,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"最好習近平繼續做 百年一遇既昏君"},{"pid":"36d36675cdec13966bcc48b53f3737462501b204","tid":2080024,"uid":140737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"共產黨黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aac535c33d0ad42a84348c90b531f3e3b148d06","tid":2080024,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"斷六親唔會有用,中共不嬲有殺錯冇放過"}]}